def transform_dataset(input_list):
    subjects = sorted(list(set([entry[1] for entry in input_list])))
    students = sorted(list(set([entry[0] for entry in input_list])))
    
    # Initialize output list with the header
    output_list = [[''] + subjects]
    
    # Populate scores for each student
    for student in students:
        score_row = [student] + [''] * len(subjects)
        
        for entry in input_list:
            if entry[0] == student:
                subject_index = subjects.index(entry[1]) + 1
                score_row[subject_index] = entry[2]
        
        output_list.append(score_row)
    
    return output_list
